 From The Economist magazine  
 c.2000 Economist Newspaper Ltd.  
<TEXT>
 &UR; (Distributed by the New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC;
<P>
   (UNDATED) _ One of the good things about politicians is that you
can poke fun at them. Humor helps to puncture pomposity, alleviate
