<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-26 14:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2133 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-TECH-NAPSTER-2TAKES-B     09-26 1593
