<P>
   FBN-PATRIOTS-COMMENT ((Miami) _ It has come down to this for the
Patriots. It has come down to a wing (Drew Bledsoe's) and a prayer
(Lawyer Milloy's). By Ron Borges.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
