<P>
   There's great foliage in Canada and one of the best ways to
enjoy it is with a stay at one of Fairmont Hotels &AMP; Resorts' famed
Quebec properties: Le Chateau Frontenac in Quebec City, Le Manoir
Richelieu in Charlevoix, and Le Chateau Montebello or The Queen
Elizabeth in Montreal. Each hotel has special values for the
seasons. For information, call 800-441-1414.
