   The Wequassett Inn in Chatham is offering a golf package that
includes a round of golf at Cape Cod National, which was recently
voted one of the top five private courses in the country by Golf
Digest. The package, through Oct. 12, is $389 a night based on a
two-night stay, and is $339 a night Oct. 13-28. Taxes are extra.
Call 800-225-7125 or visit www.
