   CHINA-ROCK-CONCERT (Beijing) _ At the first mega-band rock
concert allowed to grace a stadium in the nation's capital since
the spring of 1989, a horde of bands making up for lost time forced
themselves upon a crowd that, at certain moments, didn't seem to
know what had hit them. By Jonathan Ansfield.
</P>
