   PRAGUE-PROTESTS (Prague) _ Czechs watch with anger as some 5,000
anticapitalist activists march on the IMF and World Bank summit,
throwing firebombs and rocks at riot police and doing the ritual
trashing of a McDonalds. By Brian Whitmore. 800 words.
