<P>
   NURSING-EDEN _ ALEXANDRIA, Va. _ The expansive country kitchen,
with windows overlooking a flowering garden and a cat curled up on
a nearby sofa, hardly looked like the dreaded image of a nursing
home. Residents of Goodwin House are part of a movement to bring
more humanity, respect and companionship, as well as animals,
plants and children, into nursing facilities. (Malone, Cox News
