   BBC's quiz tests Olympic knowledge
</P>
<P>
   So you think you know about the Olympics? The BBC's Barry Davies
has a multiple choice quiz that will test your knowledge about the
Games. Every day until the closing ceremony, Davies will post three
new questions. Click by the answers of your choice, then submit
them to see how you fared.
</P>
<P>
   www.bbc.co.uk
</P>
<P>
   EVENTS
</P>
<P>
   LANCE ARMSTRONG: The Olympic cyclist and cancer survivor will
discuss his experiences during a live, one-hour chat from Sydney.
</P>
<P>
   5 p.m. at www.nbcolympics.com
</P>
