<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SENATE CLEARS HURDLE ON BILL TO EXPAND FOREIGN VISAS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
