   Eastman Kodak revamps Web site
</P>
<P>
   Eastman Kodak Co., which has been investing in companies that
store and print photos on the Internet, has revamped its Web site
to let users store, edit and share photographs.
</P>
<P>
   www.kodak.com
</P>
