<SLUG> BC-HARVARD-RUSSIA-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
U.S. SEEKS MILLIONS IN SUIT AGAINST ADVISERS TO RUSSIA 
</HEADLINE>
  (Eds: Also being filed in `a' category.) 
 By CAREY GOLDBERG   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON _ Federal prosecutors filed a civil suit Tuesday
