   (OLY19) SYDNEY, Australia -- Sept. 26, 2000 -- OLY-BASEBALL-3 --
Tommy Lasorda, manager of the United States baseball team, before
their game against South Korea. The wettest and wackiest game in
Olympic baseball history ended with a solo homer in the ninth
inning to beat South Korea 3-2 in the semifinals early Wednesday in
Sydney. (Joey Ivansco/Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   (OLY18) UNDATED -- Sept. 26, 2000 -- OLY-BASEBALL-2 -- Doug
Mientkiewicz raises his arm in celebration of his game-winning home
