early Wednesday in Sydney. Mientkiewicz, the first baseman who was
banished to the Minnesota Twins' farm system this season, ended the
wettest and wackiest game in Olympic baseball history with a solo
homer in the ninth inning to beat South Korea 3-2 in the
semifinals. (Joey Ivansco/Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
